@startuml
title scraping - 채용공고 자동 수집 Celery Worker 내부 구조

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  BorderColor #2196F3
}
skinparam component<<external>> {
  BackgroundColor #ECEFF1
  BorderColor #607D8B
}
skinparam component<<plugin>> {
  BackgroundColor #FFF9C4
  BorderColor #FBC02D
}
skinparam component<<llm>> {
  BackgroundColor #FFF3E0
  BorderColor #FB8C00
}

queue "Redis\n(scraping queue)" as Redis <<external>>
component "Backend\n(결과 콜백 task)" as BE <<external>>
component "Target Site\n(JobKorea · JobPlanet · ...)" as Site <<external>>
component "LLM Gateway\n(OpenAI via LiteLLM)" as LLM <<llm>>
database "PostgreSQL\n(direct write)" as DB <<external>>

package "scraping/" {
  component "celery_app.py\nconfig.py" as Cfg
  component "tasks.py\n(BaseTask: scrape_url)" as Task
  component "pipeline.py\n(Extract → Transform → Load)" as Pipeline
  component "scraper.py\n(httpx fallback chain →\nPlaywright headless)" as Scraper

  package "plugins/ (Site-Specific Strategy)" {
    component "registry.py\n(Plugin lookup)" as PReg
    component "base.py\n(SitePlugin ABC)" as PBase
    component "jobkorea.py" as PJK <<plugin>>
    component "jobplanet.py" as PJP <<plugin>>
    component "default.py\n(fallback)" as PDef <<plugin>>
  }

  package "extractors/" {
    component "llm_extractor.py\n(LLM 구조화 추출)" as LLMExt
    component "schema.py\n(Pydantic 출력 스키마)" as ExtSchema
  }

  component "db/\n(SQLAlchemy session)" as DBLayer
  component "schemas/\nutils/" as Misc
}

Redis --> Task : pull task
Task --> Pipeline : run(url)
Pipeline --> Scraper : fetch
Scraper --> Site : httpx GET / Playwright load
Scraper --> PReg : lookup(url)
PReg --> PJK
PReg --> PJP
PReg --> PDef
PJK --> PBase
PJP --> PBase
PDef --> PBase

Pipeline --> LLMExt : raw HTML / text
LLMExt --> LLM : prompt + Pydantic schema
LLMExt ..> ExtSchema : validate

Pipeline --> DBLayer : upsert JobPosting
DBLayer --> DB
Task --> Redis : callback (Backend collect_callback)
Redis --> BE

footer scraping/ — Strategy Pattern (plugins) · httpx → Playwright fallback · LLM 구조화 추출
@enduml
